overview: Nightveil: Witchwar is a full-color, live-action movie that brings AC Comics popular Femforce character Nightveil to life, in a wild, way-out feature-length movie that recounts her origin (see her learn the ways of sorcery from the other-worldly wizard known as Azagoth, and evolve from the two-fisted crimefighter known as Blue Bulleteer, into Nightveil, Sorceress Supreme!!)
title: Nightveil: Witchwar
